{"serial": "21037", "department_serial": 20, "code": "MA3123", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Topics in Financial Mathematics I", "ch": "金融數學專題Ⅰ"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chen, Ting-Fu"], "ch": ["陳亭甫"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["7"]}, "loc": {"building": "M", "room": "328"}}, {"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "M", "room": "328"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "數學系", "en": "Department of Mathematics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 37, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程旨在培養學生深入理解和應用進階金融模型的能力，並結合程式技能解決金融市場中的複雜問題。透過專題研究，學習如何運用數值方法評價選擇權、進行風險管理、分析波動度、建構風險中立模型，以及了解利率模型等相關主題。", "en": "This course aims to cultivate students‘ ability to understand and apply advanced financial models and integrate programming skills to solve problems in the financial markets. Through project research, students will learn how to use numerical methods for option pricing, manage risks, analyze volatility, construct risk-neutral models, and understand interest rate models."}, "outline": {"ch": "本課程為金融數學領域的相關應用，帶領學生進行專題研究與實作，涵蓋的主題可包含但不限於以下內容: 以數值方法評價衍生性商品、不同評價方法的比較、新奇選擇權評價與避險、模型的參數估計與校準、進階模型的衍生性商品評價與避險誤差、隱含波動度曲面配適、風險中立下的報酬率分布研究、最小變異避險、殖利率曲線校準、利率模型下的債券評價、或其他金融數學相關主題。", "en": "This course aims to practical applications of financial mathematics, guiding students in research projects and implementations. Topics covered may include, but are not limited to:\n1. Numerical valuation of derivative securities.\n2. Comparison of different valuation methodologies.\n3. Pricing and hedging of exotic options.\n4. Parameter estimation and calibration.\n5. Derivative pricing and hedging errors under advanced models.\n6. Investigating the implied volatility surface and the risk-neutral probability distribution.\n7. Minimum variance hedging.\n8. Yield curve calibration.\n9. Bond valuation under interest rate models.\n10. Other related topics in financial mathematics."}, "textbook": {"ch": "1. Steven E. Shreve, Stochastic Calculus for Finance II: Continuous-Time Models\n2. Python 金融分析（第二版）， Yves Hilpisch 著，賴屹民(譯)，歐萊禮出版社。", "en": "1. Steven E. Shreve, Stochastic Calculus for Finance II: Continuous-Time Models\n2. Python 金融分析（第二版）， Yves Hilpisch 著，賴屹民(譯)，歐萊禮出版社。"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "50", "en": "50"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "期中報告：30％\n期末專題：70％", "en": "Midterm Presentation:30％\nFinal Project:70％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期三下午2-3點或另約時間。", "en": "Wed. 14:00-15:00"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "金融科技相關閱讀資料", "en": "FinTech related reading material"}, "domain": {"ch": "計算數學\n\n\n、\n\n\n機率統計", "en": "計算數學\n\n\n、\n\n\n機率統計"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "發掘問題", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯分析", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "演算能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "程式實作", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "語文溝通", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "團隊合作", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "博雅通識", "rating": "(2)低", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "跨域整合", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Exploring problems", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Logical analysis", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Research Report(printed on paper)", "